    IntegrationTestTimeBoundedMultiGetRequestsWithRegionReplicas
    Extends IntegrationTestTimeBoundedRequestsWithRegionReplicas for multi-gets Besides the options already talked about in IntegrationTestTimeBoundedRequestsWithRegionReplicas the addition options here are: -DIntegrationTestTimeBoundedMultiGetRequestsWithRegionReplicas.multiget_batchsize=100 -DIntegrationTestTimeBoundedMultiGetRequestsWithRegionReplicas.num_regions_per_server=5 The multiget_batchsize when set to 1 will issue normal GETs.
